<br>
And for some unsolicited moralizing, takes two to fight, and one to make a peace offering. I guess everyone draws their own line about where they will and won't go in defense of their honor. It's just too bad that there's a bunch of relatively innocent people who'll end up being the focus of a game of tit for tat. Sounds like both parties are letting themselves sink to a lower standard than they usually hold themselves to. Personally, the person/guild who makes the selfless gesture gets respect from me. <br>
<br>
Aeloryn Dreamsculptor, 60 Enchanter<br>
